USE CASE DAIGRAMS
Is a type of unified modelling language that shows how users interact with a system through use cases.
PURPOSE
.show functional requirememts 
.help stakeholders and developers communicate clearly
.provide a high level view of system interactions
BENEFITS
.captures systems scope clearly
.helps identify functional requirements early
.improves communication betqqween users and developers
